snippet.title: Academy of Champions Football - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Discover Academy of Champions Football, the arcade football game featuring Pelé and Mia Hamm. Developed for the Wii™ system from Nintendo, Academy of Champions is scheduled to be released in 2009.
